data.description: Check out this rural paradise on 2.42 acres on a quiet street. Brand new roof and newer AC and appliances! Three bedroom two bath home with an oversized two car garage and shed both with electric and overhead fans. Large walk in master closet and sunroom. Bath tub/shower as well as another shower located in master bathroom. Guest bathroom also has bathtub/shower. Carport next to the garage for extra parking. Nice front porch to enjoy morning coffee. Property is partially fenced already, and backs up to a woodline so lots of privacy. This is the perfect opportunity for anyone that wants to live in the country. Just minutes to the springs and the nature coast, as well as under an hour drive to Ocala and just over an hour to Tampa. Close to the Suncoast for easy commuting. Lot is mostly flat so perfect for animals, gardening, or whatever you have in mind.  Call today to make your private appointment! MLS Entry Only. For Sale By Owner.  Call seller directly.  Listing brokerage does not represent seller.
